reviewText: great dvd,great songs,great music! the two times ive seen these guys live was just as good, i wish they would come back to burts tiki lounge in salt lake city! the drinks are on me! its cool to find a unique band that knows how to write and play very well, i would recomend this dvd to anyone who truly appreciates blue grass mixed with lyrics about killing your cheatin girlfriend, the pine box boys are an amazing band!!!
